content:
A one out of one panel put onto the blockchain from Saiba Gang's first manga episode: The Mistake. 

This first episode was a mysterious look into the Saiba Gang world that has left everyone hooked and ready to see more.

Each manga release will come with 1/1 NFTs for each panel in that episode. The rare Saiba Gang holders who receive one will have a commemorative piece for what will be developing into a truly epic story, crafted by @JessArtemisia and illustrated by @ElhoudDouaa.

A one out of one panel put onto the blockchain from Saiba Gang's second manga episode: The Beginning.
